/************* javascript *****************/

it is important to know the difference beetween && and & operators which is seen in package.json as 

"compile_and_watch": "npm run tsc-watch & npm run watchifyMe"

&& IS AND CONDITIONAL operator once one script doesnt produce error it will run next , 
& operator will run both scripts regardeless the outcome of the first one 

